          "role": "body",
          "order": 1,
          "align": "left",
          "original_text": "The Florida Small Business Emergency Bridge Loan program provides short-term,\nzero-interest working capital loans that are intended to “bridge the gap” between the time a\ndisaster impacts a business and when a business has secured longer term recovery funding\nsuch as federally or commercially available loans, insurance claims or other resources.",
          "translated_text": ""
        },
        {
